%% RHOAI Operator (rhods-operator) - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as Gateway (Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS Terminate
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS (service-CA)
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth /<br/>External OIDC<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Backend Component<br/>Service
    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as RHOAI Operator
    participant Nginx as dashboard-redirect<br/>nginx<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Backend: Flow 1: User Access via Gateway (LoadBalancer Mode)
    User->>Gateway: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)
    Gateway->>AuthProxy: ext_authz check (HTTPS/8443, service-CA TLS)
    AuthProxy->>OAuth: OAuth2/OIDC Flow (HTTPS/443)
    OAuth-->>AuthProxy: Auth Token
    AuthProxy-->>Gateway: Auth Result + Headers
    Gateway->>Backend: Forward Request (Bearer Token via Lua filter)
    Backend-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over User,Backend: Flow 2: User Access via Gateway (OcpRoute Mode)
    User->>Router: HTTPS/443 (Edge/Reencrypt TLS)
    Router->>Gateway: Reencrypt TLS (HTTPS/443)
    Gateway->>AuthProxy: ext_authz check (HTTPS/8443)
    AuthProxy->>OAuth: OAuth2/OIDC Flow (HTTPS/443)
    OAuth-->>AuthProxy: Auth Token
    AuthProxy-->>Gateway: Auth Result
    Gateway->>Backend: Forward (Bearer Token)
    Backend-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over Admin,Operator: Flow 3: Component Deployment
    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create/Update DSC CR (HTTPS/6443, Bearer Token)
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event (ServiceAccount Token)
    Operator->>Operator: Reconcile Component Controllers
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Resources (HTTPS/6443, SA Token)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resource Created

    Note over User,Nginx: Flow 4: Dashboard Legacy Redirect
    User->>Router: HTTPS/443 (legacy dashboard route)
    Router->>Nginx: HTTP/8080 (plaintext)
    Nginx-->>User: 301 Redirect to rh-ai.{domain}
